{"tid":2197720,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有迪士尼高層回應點解《花木蘭》鳴謝新疆部門","createTime":"2020-09-10T23:26:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T09:53:46.000Z","uid":41343,"like":4,"dislike":319,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"28857dcc5ec2ca8707b02fdb182c75035d52f709","tid":2197720,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T23:26:54.000Z","msg":"&lsquo;Mulan&rsquo;: Disney CFO Christine McCarthy Concedes China Uproar &ldquo;Has Generated A Lot Of Issues For Us&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://deadline.com/2020/09/mulan-disney-cfo-christine-mccarthy-concedes-china-uproar-has-generated-a-lot-of-issues-for-us-1234574761/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2020%2F09%2Fmulan-disney-cfo-christine-mccarthy-concedes-china-uproar-has-generated-a-lot-of-issues-for-us-1234574761%2F&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FI6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=ca77d228\" target=\"_blank\">https://deadline.com/2020/09/mulan-disney-cfo-christine-mccarthy-concedes-china-uproar-has-generated-a-lot-of-issues-for-us-1234574761/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n &ldquo;Let me just put something into context. The real facts are that Mulan was primarily shot &mdash; almost in entirety &mdash; in New Zealand. In an effort to accurately depict some of the unique landscape and geography of the country of China for this period drama, we filmed scenery in 20 different locations in China. It&rsquo;s common knowledge that, in order to film in China, you have to be granted permission. That permission comes from the central government.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nMcCarthy went on, noting that it is a common practice around the world &ldquo;to acknowledge in a film&rsquo;s credits the national and local governments that allowed you to film there. So, in our credits, it recognized both China and locations in New Zealand. I would just leave it at that, but it has generated a lot of issues for us.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"7adcea3c842849587f6008fb57e9ab3ed3e91f8d",